item.title: About
item.description: Rainbow Health International PTE.LTD is a distribution agent and service provider in the field of healthcare. With offices in Beijing and outlets in Continental Europe and UK/Ireland, we have an extensive knowledge of cross-continent healthcare needs, and have been providing PPE to markets and institutions across the World. Connecting Medical Supplies companies directly to producers, guaranteeing product scrutiny, lead time analysis, and handling delivery agencies where required, Rainbow Health International can provide a producer to market service on a daily basis.
